{"tid":908901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"地產狗開單血淚史 ：「卑微得如陰毛，同時又重要得如神父」","createTime":"2018-11-20T02:50:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T11:59:47.000Z","uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a20c92d3c2ad664a19f58c12caba86ebbb1c9860","tid":908901,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T02:50:54.000Z","msg":"每逢有新樓盤開賣，大家的焦點除了放在破記錄的呎價和不合常理的單位間隔之外，一眾地產代理的行為都令人咋舌：拔足狂奔追車、發動人海圍攻客人、左一拳右一拳齊打交。這些片段都曾在網上瘋傳。不少人討厭，甚至蔑視地產代理這個行業。但其實，放下尊嚴搶客的背後，都是為了生計。<br />\n<br />\n入行近十年的「地產仔」含淚向我們剖白，認為地產代理一職往往被人輕視，但其職能又十分重要。<span style=\"color: red;\">他打了一比喻：卑微得如陰毛，同時又重要得如神父。</span>這行搵食艱難，不少代理只拿着一份低過最低工資的底薪，唯有勇悍到底，搏盡搶客開單。雖然網民恥笑打架、圍人的行為，但在「地產仔」眼中，「真係有客欣賞㗎」......<br />\n<br />\n製作：Irene方嘉"},{"pid":"18f98eb5655367a92467bf5dbf5ec06e940d7a78","tid":908901,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T02:54:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SynH1iblgqI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSynH1iblgqI&d=6bPelPYNlKPQ9BKRbB%2BhvQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=eab979f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SynH1iblgqI</a>"},{"pid":"aacb4810185bbdd3ea05d8e1f24ef3ce0cd21212","tid":908901,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T02:56:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LsbZxkMtUWM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLsbZxkMtUWM&d=6bPelPYNlKPQ9BKRbB%2BhvQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=ff4fc27b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LsbZxkMtUWM</a>"},{"pid":"f171671773c6c654050f9669d7698128a281ce71","tid":908901,"uid":73718,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T03:07:37.000Z","msg":"食屎啦，0技術，剩係靠吹，你都係搏開大單，鬼有人做咩"},{"pid":"4f0ebf2d8271ec36587924da1ccfb1e731c5a39a","tid":908901,"uid":4942,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T03:09:39.000Z","msg":"收皮啦<br />